    <p>"Cockatoo" isn't one bird. The five species people actually cross-shop against a Grey differ as much from one another as they do from the Grey — in size, volume and temperament. Here's the honest head-to-head for each, using the photos our buyers send us. If you searched a specific matchup like African Grey vs Umbrella cockatoo or African Grey vs Galah, start here.</p>
