    <h2 class="cag-h2">What One Family Said After Choosing the Grey</h2>
    <p>We've guided a decade of these Grey-or-cockatoo decisions, and the pattern is consistent enough that we'll put our own name to it. The verified buyer reviews — real names, real cities — live on our <a href="/african-grey-reviews/">African Grey reviews</a> page.</p>
